            <lang xml:lang="en">SSP 302 is a switch, mains powered plug-in device that supports energy monitoring and measure electrical parameters as well as it acts as a repeater in a Z-Wave network. </lang>
          </description>
            <wakeupNote>
            <lang xml:lang="en"></lang>
          </wakeupNote>
            <inclusionNote>
            <lang xml:lang="en">Press and
hold the button on SSP 302 for 4 to 7 seconds
then release. The network status LED will start
flashing (twice per second) on successful start of
inclusion process.</lang>
          </inclusionNote>
